text: Tyler Abell (born 9 August 1932)Profile of Tyler Abell is an American lawyer and politician. He was the Chief of Protocol of the United States during the Lyndon B. Johnson presidency from 1968 until 1969. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1932 births Category:Lawyers from Washington, D.C. Category:Politicians from Washington, D.C.
